<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-2')">2</a>. Who <em>as you remember</em> was named Reginald</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-3"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-3')">3</a>. The family trip to Saturn did not go well. It was smoggy, wet; didn't support human life at all. The worst part was when they found out that the jewelry store was closed. It was strange, their advertisement about rings was still up.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-4"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-4')">4</a>. With his <em>metal wheels</em> and his <em>lumbar supporting back</em>. Absolutely shameful.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-5"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-5')">5</a>. The hand notably does not reflect light in the visible spectrum.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-6"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-6')">6</a>. Involving a masseuse, a brown M&amp;M, and a parcheesy game</div>
